    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid, well-kept condition\u2014super clean inside and out, and it runs like a champ! It\u2019s been well-loved and is totally ready for its next owner to hit the road. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks fantastic and handles beautifully, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
