    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal. The exterior paint retains a beautiful luster, with only minor, age-appropriate imperfections such as small stone chips on the hood that do not detract from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; all power features, including the climate control and infotainment system, operate exactly as they should. The upholstery is free of tears, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster from careful use. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, benefiting from a consistent service schedule and a recent professional inspection. It handles with precision, brakes firmly, and the engine runs smoothly without any underlying issues. This is a turn-key vehicle, complete with a full folder of maintenance records, ready to provide its next owner with many miles of dependable service.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated styling. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure peak operational performance. Featuring a clean interior and a well-preserved exterior, it offers a premier driving experience for the discerning owner. We invite you to experience the superior handling and robust engineering of this exceptional automotive offering.",
      "price": 34800.0,
