    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's been well-loved and is ready for its next big adventure? This beauty runs like a dream and has been kept in really solid shape over the years. It\u2019s perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love how it handles. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
