    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional volumetric efficiency. The power is sent to the rear wheels via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock. Notable mechanical stewardship includes a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed rod bearings, ensuring the structural and internal integrity of the platform. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the tactile feedback and neutral handling balance the E46 is renowned for. While the exterior reflects its history as a driver's car, the drivetrain remains robust, with a linear power band that pulls strongly to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
